Corporate Strategy & Innovation                                          CONFIDENTIAL

EXECUTIVE STRATEGY OFFSITE SUBMISSION
2025 Strategic Roadmap

Date: September 12, 2024
Author: M. Delgado, VP Corporate Strategy
Classification: Strictly Confidential – Executive Leadership Only

================================================================================
1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
================================================================================
The 2025 strategy refresh positions the firm to capture adjacent market share in the
Intelligent Supply Chain (ISC) segment while modernizing our core Decision Analytics
platform. This roadmap outlines five strategic initiatives, their quarterly milestones,
resource requirements, and foundational technology enablers. Total incremental budget
requested: $8.7M, with 18 net-new hires across data engineering, AI/ML, and strategic
partner management.

================================================================================
