================================================================================
  Initiative Name              Owner                 Scope
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Project Lighthouse           C. Vance              AI-driven supply chain risk scoring engine
  Digital Twin Accelerator     J. Okonkwo            Real-time logistics simulation for top 50 clients
  Horizon Analytics Refresh    R. Singh              Migration of legacy dashboards to cloud-native stack
  Partner Ecosystem 2.0        L. Chen               Co-innovation program with 8 strategic vendors
  Talent & Culture 2025        K. Nakamura           Upskilling, rotational programs, and DEI hiring

================================================================================
3. MILESTONES & TIMELINE (FY2025)
================================================================================
Q1 (Oct-Dec 2024)
  - Lighthouse: Complete data lake ingestion for 12 supplier tiers.
  - Digital Twin: Pilot twin model for Acme Industrial & Roadway Dynamics.
  - Horizon: Containerize 60% of existing Tableau workloads.
  - Ecosystem: Sign terms with VorTech Systems and NuraLogix.
  - Talent: Launch internal AI residency cohort of 5.

Q2 (Jan-Mar 2025)
  - Lighthouse: Beta release of risk scoring algorithm; accuracy target >94%.
  - Digital Twin: Expand to 10 clients; integrate real-time weather APIs.
  - Horizon: Deploy Kubernetes cluster in us-east4; decommission 4 on-prem servers.
  - Ecosystem: Joint go-to-market campaigns with 4 partners; shared pipeline of $22M.
  - Talent: Bring onboard 8 new data engineers and 2 AI product managers.

Q3 (Apr-Jun 2025)
  - Lighthouse: General availability (GA) release; integrate with SAP S/4HANA clients.
  - Digital Twin: Launch self-service simulation portal for client strategists.
  - Horizon: Full sunset of legacy stack; all 220 dashboards live on new platform.
  - Ecosystem: Co-patent filing for predictive maintenance algorithm with NuraLogix.
  - Talent: Executive immersion program for 15 high-potential leaders.

Q4 (Jul-Sep 2025)
  - Lighthouse: Reach 100 paying enterprise tenants.
  - Digital Twin: Achieve $4.2M in attributable contract value.
  - Horizon: Pass SOC 2 Type II audit on new environment.
  - Ecosystem: Establish joint venture with VorTech Systems for APAC market.
  - Talent: Year-end review; measure retention improvement of 12%.

